        "url": {
          "raw": "{{API_ROOT}}/api/contacts",
          "host": ["{{API_ROOT}}"],
          "path": ["api", "contacts"]
        },
        "description": "## 에러 케이스: 필수 필드 누락\n\n필수 필드: name, email, inquiryType, country, subject, message\n\n## 예상 응답\n```json\n{\n  \"data\": null,\n  \"error\": {\n    \"status\": 400,\n    \"name\": \"BadRequestError\",\n    \"message\": \"Validation failed\",\n    \"details\": {\n      \"errors\": [\"Valid email is required\", \"Inquiry type is required\", ...]\n    }\n  }\n}\n```"
      }
    },
